<div class="content-inner">




<div class="question">
<h2 class="question-title">瞎扯 · 为什么水系魔法师不直接把敌人体内的水抽干完成击杀，而是要控制好几吨水去砸人?</h2>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fc734cfcc0b308e24640f9b5a2d2316d_l.jpg?source=8673f162">
<span class="author">知乎日报</span>
<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/None/answer/None" class="originUrl" hidden>查看知乎原文</a>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/511160529/answer/1979222653240882342" target="_blank"> 为什么水系魔法师不直接把敌人体内的水抽干完成击杀，而是要控制好几吨水去砸人?</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/eac36493d99697f6ea103b5d90a533cb" target="_blank">@赤座灯里</a> ：你不讲规矩，那么大家也不讲规矩了</div>
火系：人体自燃、人体温度将至冰点。<br>风系：空气不进肺、高速气流制造超低压环境<br>土系：控制肾结石在尿道来回滑动。矿物质凝聚组赛动脉<br>要么见面秒，要么被暗杀。生在这个环境里,死得随意,死得抽象,死得莫名其妙<br>毁灭吧，累了</blockquote>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/488414346/answer/3206802396" target="_blank">什么东西曾经离谱的贵，现在却非常便宜或者没人感兴趣了？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/6c4722f0a0dee029532b217ddfa9a232" target="_blank">@沈伟 will</a> ：</div>
</blockquote>
